<div class="title">A Bender to Remember!!!</div>
<div class="substance">Alcohol, Cannabis & Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Nekom&Exact=1">Nekom</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Nekom. "A Bender to Remember!!!: An Experience with Alcohol, Cannabis & Caffeine (exp2290)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 16, 2000. erowid.org/exp/2290</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
